                                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-user"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span><strong>Department / Designation / Grade: </strong><span id="DepartmentName" class="DepartmentName"></span> <strong> / </strong> <span><span id="DesignationName" class="DesignationName"></span></span><strong> / </strong><span><span id="GradeName" class="GradeName"></span></span></span><br />
